Understanding the discrepancy between our re-analysis of vQTL data and EB-IPSC analysis

First, does running more tests make a huge difference? 1. Subset to the intersection of tests run in both analyses 2. Perform MTC again 3. Compare the number of hits

overlap_tests <- intersect(ebqtl_strict_all$gv, vqtl_all$gv)
overlap_tests <- intersect(overlap_tests, ebqtl_all$gv)
overlap_tests <- intersect(overlap_tests, ebqtl_tmm_all$gv)

ebqtl_overlap <- filter(ebqtl_all, gv %in% overlap_tests) # 915000 of 1965203
